    <item>
      <title>赛诺菲医疗竞标者因滑石粉问题修改报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/sanofi-healthcare-bidders-revising-offers-over-talc-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，赛诺菲消费者保健部门的竞标者正在修改其报价，部分原因是为了解决对销售滑石粉的品牌可能产生的责任的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/sanofi-healthcare-bidders-revising-offers-over-talc-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 16:34:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
