      <title>Elis 结束与美国竞争对手 UniFirst、Vestis 的收购谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/elis-scraps-acquisition-talks-with-us-rivals-unifirst-vestis</link>
